<exercise checkit-seed="0005" checkit-slug="P5" checkit-title="Expected Value">
    <statement>
                <p> Dennis is gambling \$8 on rolling a 6 on a 13-sided die. If Dennis wins, they win \$20, otherwise they forfit their bet. What is the expected value of this gamble?
                </p>
        
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p>
            The expected value is <me>\frac{1}{13}(20) + \frac{12}{13}(-8) = -$5.85</me>
        </p>
    </answer>
</exercise>
